s%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fin-silicon-valley-it-is-the-summer-of-fomo-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epaying%20top%20dollar%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20recruit%20elite%20AI%20talent%2C%20a%20trend%20that's%20likened%20to%20sports%20franchises%20competing%20for%20superstar%20athletes%20like%20Cristiano%20Ronaldo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20competition%20reached%20another%20level%20when%20Meta%20recruited%20Scale's%20CEO%2C%20Alexandr%20Wang%2C%20last%20month%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%2414.3%20billion%20deal%20to%20take%20a%2049%25%20stake%20in%20his%20company.%20Then%2C%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20said%20Meta%20had%20tried%20to%20poach%20his%20best%20employees%20with%20%24100%20million%20signing%20bonuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20weeks%20ago%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-in-tech-are-worried-windsurf-has-set-dangerous-precedent-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%20paid%20%242.4%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20hire%20the%20CEO%20and%20top%20talent%20of%20AI%20startup%20Windsurf%20and%20license%20its%20intellectual%20property.%20OpenAI%20had%20planned%20to%20buy%20Windsurf%20for%20%243%20billion%2C%20but%20the%20deal%20fell%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20typical%20way%20of%20doing%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20Jian%20said%20of%20Big%20Tech's%20hiring%20strategy.%20Chasing%20the%20same%20pool%20of%20in-demand%20talent%20isn't%20always%20a%20winning%20move%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20everybody%20knows%20that%20these%20are%20talents%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20better%20for%20you%20not%20to%20get%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20about%20the%20vision%2C%20you%20know%2C%20where%20you%20want%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20and%20Alibaba%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222782d601-3944-48b1-be4f-2ccb4d92c14c%5C%22%3EChina's%20AI%20race%20is%20'very%20healthy'%20competition%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20also%20said%20that%20the%20rivalry%20among%20Chinese%20AI%20firms%20is%20not%20cutthroat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20single%20person%20or%20company%20can%20sprint%20forever%2C%20he%20said.%20But%20collectively%2C%20the%20ecosystem%20can%20still%20move%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20a%20pattern%20he's%20observed%3A%20One%20company%20surges%20ahead%2C%20then%20slows.%20Then%20another%20takes%20the%20lead.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20first%20catches%20up%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20have%20the%20very%20fast%20iteration%20of%20the%20technology%20because%20of%20this%20competition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it's%20brutal%2C%20but%20I%20think%20it's%20very%20healthy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20biggest%20tech%20players%20have%20focused%20on%20open-source%20AI%20models%2C%20which%20have%20code%20and%20architecture%20that%20are%20publicly%20available%20for%20anyone%20to%20use%2C%20modify%2C%20or%20build%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20analyst%20told%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20that%20Chinese%20firms%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-deepseek-integrate-ai-consolidation-us-openai-paywall-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprioritizing%20consolidation%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20stay%20competitive.%20For%20instance%2C%20Tencent%20has%20deployed%20its%20Hunyuan%20model%20and%20DeepSeek%20R1%20across%20its%20massive%20ecosystem%2C%20including%20WeChat.%20Baidu%20has%20also%20integrated%20DeepSeek%20R1%20into%20its%20search%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20is%20closing%20the%20gap%20with%20the%20US%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Stratechery%20interview%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Nvidia's%20CEO%2C%20Jensen%20Huang%2C%20said%20that%20China%20is%20doing%20%26quot%3Bfantastic%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20AI%20market%2C%20with%20homegr