0Airbus%20planes%20on%20its%20website%2C%20has%20been%20mostly%20operating%20domestic%20routes%20in%20the%20meantime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20first%20flight%20to%20North%20Korea%20left%20Moscow%20at%207%3A25%20p.m.%20on%20Sunday%20and%20arrived%20in%20Pyongyang%20at%203%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Moscow%20Sheremetyevo%20International%20Airport's%20flight%20tracker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20return%20flight%20is%20scheduled%20for%20Tuesday.%20TASS%20reported%20that%20both%20flights%2C%20with%20tickets%20costing%20about%20%24550%2C%20were%20fully%20booked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20is%20the%20first%2021st-century%20flight%20between%20both%20capitals%2C%20Russians%20could%20already%20fly%20to%20North%20Korea%20before%20this.%20A%20North%20Korean%20airline%2C%20Air%20Koryo%2C%20operates%20flights%20from%20Pyongyang%20to%20Vladivostok%2C%20a%20Russian%20city%20on%20the%20Sea%20of%20Japan%20that's%20roughly%2080%20miles%20from%20North%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20newest%20flight%20is%20a%20further%20sign%20of%20rapport%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorth-koreas-learning-valuable-skills-fighting-ukraine-us-warns-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussia%20and%20North%20Korea%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20latter%20of%20which%20has%20been%20supplying%20the%20Kremlin%20with%20troops%2C%20weapons%2C%20and%20ammunition%20to%20maintain%20its%20offensive%20pace%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20partnership%20is%20sparking%20deep%20concern%20in%20the%20West%20and%20South%20Korea%2C%20which%20fear%20the%20arrangement%20is%20bolstering%20the%20technical%20expertise%20and%20resources%20of%20North%20Korea's%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENordwind's%20cross-capital%20flight%20also%20comes%20as%20North%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20has%20pushed%20hard%20to%20reopen%20his%20country%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorth-korea-open-to-foreign-tourists-again-after-5-years-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C