3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20ability%20to%20sell%20cars%20in%20California%20hangs%20in%20the%20balance%20after%20a%20weeklong%20court%20hearing%20that%20ended%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20terminology%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdriving-assistance-systems-may-create-more-risks-than-solve-study-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edriver%20assistance%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20under%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia's%20Department%20of%20Motor%20Vehicles%20sued%20Tesla%20in%202022%20and%20is%20seeking%20to%20suspend%20Tesla's%20ability%20to%20sell%20cars%20in%20the%20state%20for%20at%20least%2030%20days%20and%20award%20consumers%20monetary%20damages.%20Following%20the%20hearing%2C%20no%20final%20ruling%20has%20been%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DMV%20suit%20alleges%20that%20the%20company%20falsely%20advertised%20its%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-fsd-diary-curiosity-amazement-shock-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFull%20Self-Driving%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-autopilot-fsd-labeling-facilities-jobs-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAutopilot%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20driver%20assistance%20technologies%2C%20misleading%20consumers%20into%20thinking%20the%20cars%20were%20more%20autonomous%20than%20they%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20comes%20at%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20for%20the%20company.%20Its%20sales%20have%20slumped%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202025%2C%20and%20its%20brand%20took%20a%20hit%20earlier%20this%20year%20after%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20the%20face%20of%20the%20White%20House%20DOGE%20Office.%20Protesters%20directed%20their%20anger%20at%20Tesla%2C%20organizing%20nationwide%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftakeaways-tesla-takedown-protests-michigan-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprotests%20at%20Tesla%20dealerships%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Tesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttorney%20Matthew%20Benedetto%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Tesla's%20legal%20team%2C%20told%20Administrative%20Judge%20Juliet%20E.%20Cox%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20company%20never%20tried%20to%20conceal%20the%20fact%20that%20its%20vehicles%20cannot%20fully%20drive%20themselves%20and%20has%20always%20informed%20buyers%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20fully%20rely%26quot%3B%20on%20FSD%20or%20Autopilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCars%20with%20Full%20Self-Driving%20capabilities%20are%20currently%20not%20capable%20of%20driving%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20Benedetto%20said%20again%20on%20Tuesday%20while%20cross-examining%20a%20witness%20brought%20to%20the%20stand%20by%20DMV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DMV%20said%20in%20its%20complaint%20that%20Tesla's%20website%20advertised%20its%20driver%20assistance%20system%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20in%202021%20and%202022%20as%20being%20%26quot%3Bdesigned%20to%20be%20able%20to%20conduct%20short%20and%20long-distance%20trips%20with%20no%20action%20required%20by%20the%20person%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20Home%20-%20All%20you%20will%20need%20to%20do%20is%20get%20in%20and%20tell%20your%20car%20where%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20says%2C%20quoting%20from%20Tesla's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20vehicles%20equipped%20with%20those%20ADAS%20features%20could%20not%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20those%20advertisements%2C%20and%20cannot%20now%2C%20operate%20as%20autonomous%20vehicles%2C%26quot%3B%20Ailene%20Short%2C%20branch%20chief%20for%20the%20licensing%20department%20at%20the%20California%20DMV%2C%20wrote%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMelanie%20Rosario%2C%20commander-sergeant%20of