%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20grim%20backdrop%2C%20Kailash%20was%20chosen%20by%20then-President%20Indira%20Gandhi%20to%20head%20the%20Project%20Tiger%20initiative%20in%201973.%20He%20was%20joined%20by%20then-cabinet%20minister%20Karan%20Singh.%20There%20was%20a%20monumental%20change%20that%20found%20its%20spark%20under%20their%20leadership%20%E2%80%94%20hunting%20was%20banned%2C%20reserves%20were%20created%2C%20and%20tiger%20numbers%20were%20resuscitated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201992%2C%20Kailash%20was%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20his%20contributions%20to%20tiger%20conservation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20passing%20of%20Kailash%20two%20years%20later%2C%20his%20son%20Pradeep%20took%20over.%20Under%20his%20leadership%2C%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20Kanha%20Jungle%20Lodge%20(set%20up%20in%201989)%20and%20Bandhavgarh%20Jungle%20Lodge%20(set%20up%20in%201990)%20%E2%80%94%20both%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%94%20saw%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F473613%2Fchlorophyll-estate-sustainable-forest-farmstay-built-on-barren-land-near-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20infusion%20of%20sustainable%20concepts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20medicinal%20plant%20gardens%2C%20solar%20cookers%2C%20and%20vermicomposting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fjamtara-wilderness-camp-2-1753447220.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jamtara%20Wilderness%20Camp%20is%20a%2010%20luxury%20tented%20camp%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20rural%20Pench%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fjamtara-wilderness-camp-2-1753447220.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fjamtara-wilder