a%20lot%20of%20methane%20getting%20released.%20Around%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20approached%20Waste%20Is%20Gold%20Technologies.%20Their%20machines%20are%20working%20well%20and%20we%E2%80%99ve%20had%20no%20complaints%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20further%20how%20beneficial%20this%20switch%20between%20machines%20has%20been%20for%20them%2C%20Setty%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20different%20about%20the%20Waste%20Is%20Gold%20composters%20is%20that%20they%20generate%20compost%20on%20the%20same%20day%20the%20organic%20waste%20is%20processed.%20In%20the%20machines%20we%20used%20earlier%2C%20it%20would%20take%20three%20days%20to%20generate%20that%20compost.%20The%20compost%20we%E2%80%99re%20generating%20is%20being%20used%20for%20landscaping%20purposes%20on%20our%20properties.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-Final-Feature-1695133328.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dealing%20with%20organic%20wet%20waste%20composting%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-Final-Feature-1695133328.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-Final-Feature-1695133328-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-Final-Feature-1695133328-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-Final-Feature-1695133328-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-Final-Feature-1695133328-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330328%5C%22%20heig