ing%20it.%20While%20Molai%20Payeng%20worked%20largely%20alone%20to%20raise%20his%20forest%2C%20Munmuni%20works%20with%20the%20community%2C%20making%20conservation%20democratic%20and%20deeply%20local.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2025%2C%20she%20represents%20a%20generation%20that%20sees%20climate%20change%20not%20as%20an%20abstract%20threat%2C%20but%20a%20lived%20experience.%20And%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20most%20vulnerable%20pockets%2C%20her%20green%20mission%20is%20a%20quiet%20revolution%20taking%20root.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753417800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-24T172351.681-1753358102.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D475620%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Born%20on%20Majuli%20Island%2C%20Munmuni%20Payeng%20grew%20up%20watching%20floods%20wash%20away%20land%20and%20lives.%20At%2025%2C%20she%E2%80%99s%20leading%20a%20community-driven%20mission%20to%20plant%20one%20million%20native%20trees%20to%20heal%20the%20land%20and%20protect%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F475620%2Fmunmuni-payeng-assam-million-trees-flood-restoration%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%229%20Key%20Steps%20India%20Can%20Take%20for%20a%20Fair%20%26amp%3B%20Inclusive%20Clean%20Energy%20Future%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20gradually%20moving%20towards%20its%20ambitious%20climate%20goals%2C%20including%20500%20GW%20of%20non-fossil%20capacity%20by%202030%20and%20net-zero%20emissions%20by%202070.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20transition%20accelerates%2C%20it%20must%20go%20beyond%20technological%20or%20economic%20shifts%20to%20be%20just%20and%20socially%20equitable.%20Given%20that%2072%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20electricity%20is%20still%20generated%20from%20thermal%20sources%2C%20ensuring%20worker%20up